<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قال:</span> أَوترُ ثمَ أَنامُ.<span class="c5"> قال:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c1">"بالحزمِ أَخذتَ"</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وسأَل - صلى الله عليه وسلم -<span class="c5"> عمر رضوان الله عليه:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
